<paragraph id="IFRIC01_IE8" base="SL33864"><paranum>IE8</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRIC 1"/><data name="paranum" value="IE8"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRIC01_P0089">Assume that a market&#x2011;based discounted cash flow valuation of CU115,000 is obtained at 31 December 2002. It includes an allowance of CU11,600 for decommissioning costs, which represents no change to the original estimate, after the unwinding of three years&#x2019; discount. The amounts included in the statement of financial position at 31 December 2002 are therefore: </p><table id="IFRIC01_TAB0003" base="SL76019" frame="none" orient="port"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colnum="1" colname="C1" colwidth="85*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="2" colname="C2" colwidth="15*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="right"/><tbody><row><entry colname="C1"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0090" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0091" typeface="sansserif"><b>CU</b></p></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left"> <p typeface="sansserif" id="IFRIC01_P0092" base="F611458">Asset at valuation (1) </p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0093" typeface="sansserif">126,600</p></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left"> <p typeface="sansserif" id="IFRIC01_P0094" base="F611477">Accumulated depreciation </p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0095" typeface="sansserif">nil </p></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left"> <p typeface="sansserif" id="IFRIC01_P0096" base="F611481">Decommissioning liability </p></entry><entry colname="C2" rowsep="1" align="right"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0097" typeface="sansserif">(11,600)</p></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0098" typeface="sansserif">Net assets</p></entry><entry colname="C2" rowsep="1" double_underline="yes" align="right"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0099" typeface="sansserif">115,000</p></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0100" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C2"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0101" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0102" typeface="sansserif">Retained earnings (2)</p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0103" typeface="sansserif">(10,600)</p></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0104" typeface="sansserif">Revaluation surplus (3)</p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0105" typeface="sansserif">15,600</p></entry></row><row><entry namest="C1" nameend="C2"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0106" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row keep_together="1"><entry namest="C1" nameend="C2" align="left"> <p id="IFRIC01_P0107" typeface="sansserif"><i>Notes:</i> </p></entry></row><row><entry namest="C1" nameend="C2" align="left"> <ol id="IFRIC01_L0009" base="SL146191" type="decimal"><li><li_value>1</li_value> <p id="IFRIC01_P0108" base="SL146193">Valuation obtained of CU115,000 plus decommissioning costs of CU11,600, allowed for in the valuation but recognised as a separate liability = CU126,600. </p></li><li><li_value>2</li_value> <p id="IFRIC01_P0109" base="SL146195">Three years&#x2019; depreciation on original cost CU120,000 × <sup>3</sup>/<sub>40</sub> = CU9,000  plus cumulative discount on CU10,000 at 5 per cent compound = CU1,600;  total CU10,600.</p></li><li><li_value>3</li_value> <p id="IFRIC01_P0110" base="SL146197">Revalued amount CU126,600 less previous net book value of CU111,000 (cost CU120,000 less accumulated depreciation CU9,000). </p></li></ol></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></body></paragraph>